org.jooq
Interface CaseConditionStep<T>

All Superinterfaces:
AliasProvider<Field<T>>, java.lang.Comparable<NamedQueryPart>, Field<T>, NamedQueryPart, NamedTypeProviderQueryPart<T>, QueryPartProvider
public interface CaseConditionStep<T>
extends Field<T>

The final step in creating a case statement of the type 

 CASE WHEN x < 1  THEN 'one'
      WHEN x >= 2 THEN 'two'
      ELSE            'three'
 END

Author:
Lukas Eder
